item.title: Minecraft - Mob Fireworks
item.description:
Minecraft - Mob Fireworks
Just an ordinary evening on the yogscast Minecraft server! http://yogiverse.com/pages/servers (Btw, our server is completely overloaded right now, but we're looking at getting more set up in future, as well as custom maps and skins directories, so join our community!) If you can help by hosting a server, let us know and post in the forums! How to get fireworks: 1. Install Bukkit http://bukkit.org/ 2. Download Essentials http://forums.bukkit.org/threads/gen-essentials-v2-0-286-rc2-collection-of-essential-plugins-in-one-package-531.1262/ 3. Make a glass block at the world height cap. 4. Jump down and aim at the block you just placed at the max height 5. Do /spawnmob xxx xxx (first xxx is the mobs name, second xxx is the amount of the mobs to spawn) Pro-tips: -You might have to be in the protected spawn for this to work -You may have to be on a laggy server for this to work (hahaha) -You can spawn mobs attached to other mobs by doing this /spawnmob firstmob,secondmob xxx (where xxx is the amount of the mobs you want) so you can do /spawnmob Giant,Chicken 100 for giants floating on chickens. Mob names: Chicken Cow Ghast Sheep Slime Pigzombie Giant Zombie Creeper Skeleton

item.title: Running from Tsunami: Dramatic rescue video of moments when water hit Japan
item.description:
Running from Tsunami: Dramatic rescue video of moments when water hit Japan
Follow latest updates at http://twitter.com/rt_com and http://www.facebook.com/RTnews Dramatic video has emerged from Japan of people scrambling to get onto the roof of a building to escape rapidly rising waters in the moments after the devastating tsunami struck last Friday. Following their escape, the footage then shows people attempting to save others stranded in nearby trees, and on top of cars, with the help of a hose pipe. The drama takes place in the city of Sendai against a backdrop of swirling water and devastation, cars piled up against trees and buildings.
